## Medium Severity Findings

### 5. Eager Test (Smell #5)

**Method:** `OrderProcessor_FullWorkflow_Succeeds` (line 53)

```csharp
processor.ValidateOrder(order);      // 1
processor.CalculateTotal(order);     // 2
processor.ApplyDiscount(order, …);   // 3
processor.ReserveInventory(order);   // 4
processor.ProcessPayment(order, …);  // 5
processor.SendConfirmation(order);   // 6
processor.UpdateOrderHistory(order); // 7
```

**Problem:** 7 distinct production methods in one test. When it fails, you can't tell which step broke. (testsmells.org threshold: 4+)

**Fix:** Test each step independently. If an end-to-end workflow test is needed, move it to a dedicated integration test class.

